996
01:13:47,019 --> 01:13:50,853
<i>You gotta tell me.</i>
<i>Are you</i>—<i>Are you sick? Are you in trouble?</i>

997
01:13:50,923 --> 01:13:54,859
<i>Look. Whatever it is,</i>
<i>I can handle it.</i>

998
01:13:54,927 --> 01:13:57,293
