And you have a lot of time
to think about it.

1034
01:16:26,812 --> 01:16:29,576
<i>Since I didn't have</i>
<i>anyone to share it with...</i>

1035
01:16:29,648 --> 01:16:34,608
<i>- all this pain and confusion...</i>
